Homepage: http://eugene.renice.org/spamassassin_mode_en.html

Download: http://eugene.renice.org/spamassassin-mode.el

=== Features ===

* keywords highlighting;
* templates for basic rule types;
* linting rules (via spamassassin --lint);
* optimizing regular expressions (via regex-opt utility);
* filtering message through spamassassin.

=== Configuration ===

Put spamassassin-mode.el in your <code>load-path</code> and the following in your .emacs file:

 (autoload 'spamassassin-mode "spamassassin-mode" nil t)
 (add-to-list 'auto-mode-alist 
              '("\\.cf\\'" . spamassassin-mode))

